                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ชนะโดยจำนวนตัวละครที่ถูกกำจัดต่ำกว่า 2 ตัว",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3232,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/5a18a504ec92abf9719af1ddde5ac2fd_4068886856442673021.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Strategic Reserve",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "การต่อสู้อย่างจริงจัง",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "แนะนำด่าน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"ดูเอลกับเธอนี่ต้องใช้ความคิดเยอะทีเดียวนะ แต่ว่า... จุดที่น่าสนใจมันก็อยู่ตรงนี้นี่แหละ...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "[กฎพิเศษ] ในตอนเริ่ม 'Ningguang\" จะติดตั้งการ์ดพรสวรรค์ \"Strategic Reserve\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ทีมของคู่ต่อสู้",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3191,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/04f5250a14f6693d7583630bd84d1b06_1241793201846251487.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Ningguang",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3186,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/9135fdcb8dc1dca18a13b4f4818cb2d2_516662219400051916.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Keqing",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3172,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/e5c7d702f8033c4361f3b25a7f0b8b30_86059053228619091.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Ganyu",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ปลดล็อกหลัง:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "มีเลเวลผู้เล่นถึง 7",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "สำเร็จเป้าหมายการท้าทาย Ningguang - เป็นมิตร 3 อัน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "เป้าหมายการท้าทาย",
